/**** REXX ***********************************************************/
/* Rexx                                                              */
/* Created   By :Kang Dengsong                                       */
/* Created Date :SEP 13, 2008                                        */
/* REMARK       :Job scheduler system                                */
/* ***************************************************************** */
/*================================================================*  */
/* KKKKKKKKKKKKK   DDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS                           *  */
/* KKKKKKKKKKKKK  DDDDDDDDD   SSSSSSSSS                           *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS                                *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS                                *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS          1111          0000000 *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS      1111        0000000000*  */
/*      KKKK        DDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS     1111        0000  0000*  */
/*      KKKK           DDDD        SSSS    1111         0000  0000*  */
/*      KKKK           DDDD        SSSS    1111        0000  0000 *  */
/*      KKKK           DDDD        SSSS    1111        0000  0000 *  */
/* KKK  KKKK           DDDD        SSSS   1111   0000  0000  0000 *  */
/* KKKKKKKK      DDDDDDDDDD   SSSSSSSSS   1111  0000  0000000000  *  */
/* KKKKKKKK      DDDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS    1111 0000    000000000  *  */
/*================================================================*  */
ARG JOBNAME
Address TSO
Numeric digits 64
@tcb = Get_dec_addr(540)
@jscb = Get_dec_addr(@tcb+180)
step# = Get_stor_contents(@jscb+X2d(E4) 1)
step# = X2d(C2x(step#))
@jct = Get_dec_addr(@jscb+260)
@sct = Get_dec_addr(@jct+48 3)

last_step = 'NO'
j = 1
If step# = 1 Then
  Do
    Say 'this is the first step; no rc so far --- '
    Exit
  End
Else
  Do While last_step = 'NO'
    sct_abnd = Get_Stor_Contents(@sct+176 1)
    sct_cond = Get_Stor_Contents(@sct+188 1)
    sct_rc = Get_Stor_Contents(@sct+24 2)
    If j < step# Then
      Do
        dec_Rc = Right(X2d(C2x(sct_rc)),4,'0')
        hex_Rc = C2x(sct_rc)
        prf = '8'
        ltrl = ' Rc(hex):    'hex_Rc ' Rc(dec): 'dec_Rc
      End
    Else If j = step# Then
      Do
        dec_Rc = '***'
        hex_Rc = '***'
        prf = '>'
        ltrl = ' *currently executing step* 0000'
      End
    Else
      Do
        dec_Rc = 'n/a'
        hex_Rc = 'n/a'
        prf = '1'
        ltrl = ' ***waiting for execution** WAIT'
      End
    stpnam = Get_stor_contents(@sct+68 8)
    pgmnam = Get_stor_contents(@sct+124 8)
    stpnum = Right(j,3,'0')
    lprf = prf'Schtepp 'stpnum' Stepname: 'stpnam ' Pgmname: 'pgmnam
    If Bitand(sct_cond,'10'X) = '10'X Then     /* COND-Bypass */
      ltrl = ' ***bypassed due to cond*** NOTR'
    If Bitand(sct_abnd,'04'X) = '04'X Then     /* Step Abended */
      ltrl = ' **** Jobstep abended ***** 9999'
    line = lprf''ltrl
    Say line
    @sct = Get_dec_addr(@sct+36 3)        /* sct next step */
    If @sct = 0 Then
      last_step = 'YES'
    j = j + 1
  End
RETURN
Exit
Get_dec_addr:
Parse arg value len
If len = '' Then
  len = 4
hex_value = D2x(value)
stor = Storage(hex_value,len)
hex_stor = C2x(stor)
value = X2d(hex_stor)
Return value
/* */
Get_stor_contents:
arg value length
hex_value = D2x(value)
value = Storage(hex_value,length)
Return value

              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE OR END-FILE2                KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'READ JCSFMAST NOT FOUND KEY IS= ' JCBMAST-KEY KDS08257
                 MOVE  10               TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-DTE                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE  KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-TME                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-YYYYMMDD                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-CUR-TIME                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME  KDS08257
           IF WS-RESP-2 = K                                             KDS08257
              MOVE WS-SKIP                     TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST-CKDS08257
              MOVE K                           TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS    KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE ABEND                       TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST-CKDS08257
              MOVE A                           TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCSFSPRC-STEP                  TO JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP    KDS08257
           MOVE JCSFSPRC-RC                    TO JCBMAST-ERROR-CODE    KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-MOD                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-MODE     KDS08257
           MOVE WS-NO                          TO JCBMAST-RECOVER-STS   KDS08257
      *    DISPLAY 'JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9=' JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9     KDS08257
      *    DISPLAY 'JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE-9=' JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE-9     KDS08257
           IF  JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE-9 >= 16010101 AND
               JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9 >= 16010101
           THEN
              COMPUTE WS-DAYS  =                                        KDS08257
                FUNCTION INTEGER-OF-DATE(JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE-9) -      KDS08257
                FUNCTION INTEGER-OF-DATE(JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9)        KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-DAYS  = 0                                      KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           COMPUTE JCBMAST-COST-TIME = WS-DAYS * 3600 * 24 +            KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-HH - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-HH)     KDS08257
                + 60 *                                                  KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-MM - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-MM)     KDS08257
                +                                                       KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-SS - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-SS)     KDS08257
                +                                                       KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-MS - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-MS)     KDS08257
                / 100                                                   KDS08257
           REWRITE JCBMAST-REC                                          KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'REWRITE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS    KDS08257
              MOVE     ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           IF WS-RESP-2 = K                                             KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE K              TO WS-SKIP-P                          KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-AP-SYSID   TO WS-SYSID                           KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-PROC       TO WS-PROC                            KDS08257
      *       DISPLAY 'call JCSBAPNM  in JCSBABDA begin'                KDS08257
              CALL W-JCSBAPNM USING WS-PARM                             KDS08257
      *       DISPLAY 'call JCSBAPNM  in JCSBABDA end '                 KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                     KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
      *    DISPLAY 'JCSBABDA END =' WS-RETURN-CD                        KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFSPRC                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFDTTM                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
                                                                        KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFSPRC-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFSPRC                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFSPRC-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFDTTM-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFDTTM                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFDTTM-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST.                                            KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK06.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFSPRC.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK07.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFDTTM.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK08.                                               KDS08257

      *      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS          1111          0000000 *KDS08257
      *      KKKK      DDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS      1111        0000000000*KDS08257
      *      KKKK        DDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS     1111        0000  0000*KDS08257

      ******************************************************************KDS08257
      * CREATED   BY :KANG DENGSONG                                    *KDS08257
      * CREATED DATE :SEP 13, 2008                                     *KDS08257
      * REMARK       :UPDATE MAST FILE IF ABEND                        *KDS08257
      *              :JOB SCHEDULER SYSTEM                             *KDS08257
      *================================================================*KDS08257
      *   This program is distributed without warranty of any kind,    *KDS08257

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                                            KDS08257

       CONFIGURATION SECTION.                                           KDS08257
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.                                            KDS08257
       FILE-CONTROL.                                                    KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFMAST                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFMAST-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBMAST-KEY.              KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFSPRC  ASSIGN         TO JCSFSPRC                  KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFSPRC-STS.          KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFDTTM  ASSIGN         TO JCSFDTTM                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFDTTM-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL.               KDS08257
       DATA DIVISION.                                                   KDS08257
       FILE SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
       FD JCSFMAST.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBMAST-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAST==.       KDS08257
       FD JCSFSPRC.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCSFSPRC-REC.                                                 KDS08257
          03 JCSFSPRC-STEP                   PIC X(08).                 KDS08257
          03 JCSFSPRC-RC                     PIC X(04).                 KDS08257
          03 FILLER                          PIC X(108).                KDS08257
       FD JCSFDTTM.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBDTTM-REC.                                                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-DTE                    PIC X(08).                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-TME                    PIC X(08).                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-RMD                    PIC X(64).                  KDS08257
      ******************************************************************KDS08257
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                         KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK02.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK00.                                                   KDS08257
       01 WS-RESP-2               PIC X(1) VALUE SPACE.                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-FROM-PGM.                                                KDS08257
          05 PRM-IND                      PIC X(1).                     KDS08257
          05 PRM-SYSID-PGM                PIC X(8).                     KDS08257
          05 PRM-PROC-PGM                 PIC X(8).                     KDS08257
          05 PRM-FROM-PGM                 PIC X(8).                     KDS08257
          05 PRM-RERUN-PGM                PIC 9(2).                     KDS08257
                                                                        KDS08257
       LINKAGE SECTION.                                                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
          03 PARM-LENGTH          PIC S9(4) COMP.                       KDS08257
          03 PARM-CONTENT.                                              KDS08257
             05 PRM-AP-SYSID                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-PROC                     PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-ACEPT-RC                 PIC 9(2).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-MOD                      PIC X(1).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-SKIP                     PIC X(1).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-FLG                      PIC X(1).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-RERUN-CNT                PIC 9(2).                  KDS08257
      *                                                                 KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
           DISPLAY 'JCSBABDM BEGIN '                                    KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = 0                                       KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                              KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                     KDS08257
              COPY JCSCWK05.                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                   KDS08257
              PERFORM D004-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO JOB TO PROCESS OR PARM IS INVALID'            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           READ JCSFSPRC                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFSPRC-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFSPRC ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFSPRC-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    MOVE WS-YES              TO WS-RESP                          KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSFSPRC-STEP=' JCSFSPRC-STEP ':RC=' JCSFSPRC-RC    KDS08257
           IF (JCSFSPRC-STEP = JCSPBEGN OR JCSPWARM OR JCSPWELM)        KDS08257
              AND JCSFSPRC-RC = K0093                                   KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE R                       TO WS-RESP-2                 KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF PRM-SKIP = WS-YES                                      KDS08257
TSTKDS*          MOVE K                TO WS-RESP-2                     KDS08257
                 PERFORM UNTIL WS-RESP-2 = K OR P                       KDS08257
                    DISPLAY PRM-PROC                                    KDS08257
                             ' **** ABEND ****, SKIP OR STOP(K/P)?'     KDS08257
                              UPON CONSOLE                              KDS08257
                    ACCEPT WS-RESP-2 FROM CONSOLE                       KDS08257
                 END-PERFORM                                            KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
TSTKDS*          MOVE WS-YES           TO WS-RESP                       KDS08257
                 PERFORM UNTIL WS-RESP = WS-YES OR WS-NO                KDS08257
                    DISPLAY PRM-PROC                                    KDS08257
                           ' **** ABEND ****, STOP?(Y/N)'               KDS08257
                          UPON CONSOLE                                  KDS08257
                    ACCEPT WS-RESP FROM CONSOLE                         KDS08257
                 END-PERFORM                                            KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           READ JCSFDTTM                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFDTTM-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFDTTM ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFDTTM-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D004-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-PROC                TO JCBMAST-JOB                  KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-AP-SYSID            TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID             KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY                             KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE2                           KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE OR END-FILE2                KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'READ FILE NOT FOUND KEY IS= ' JCBMAST-JOB     KDS08257
                 MOVE  10               TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-DTE                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-TME                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-9KDS08257
           MOVE WS-YYYYMMDD                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-CUR-TIME                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME  KDS08257
           IF WS-RESP-2 = K                                             KDS08257
              MOVE WS-SKIP                     TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST-CKDS08257
              MOVE K                           TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS    KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE ABEND                       TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST-CKDS08257
              MOVE A                           TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCSFSPRC-STEP                  TO JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP    KDS08257
           MOVE JCSFSPRC-RC                    TO JCBMAST-ERROR-CODE    KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-MOD                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-MODE     KDS08257
           MOVE WS-NO                          TO JCBMAST-RECOVER-STS   KDS08257
           COMPUTE WS-DAYS     =                                        KDS08257
             FUNCTION INTEGER-OF-DATE(JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE-9) -         KDS08257
             FUNCTION INTEGER-OF-DATE(JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9)           KDS08257
           COMPUTE JCBMAST-COST-TIME = WS-DAYS * 3600 * 24 +            KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-HH - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-HH)     KDS08257
                + 60 *                                                  KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-MM - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-MM)     KDS08257
                +                                                       KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-SS - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-SS)     KDS08257
                +                                                       KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-MS - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-MS)     KDS08257
                / 100                                                   KDS08257
           REWRITE JCBMAST-REC                                          KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'REWRITE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS    KDS08257
              MOVE     ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
           DISPLAY 'JCSBABDM END =' WS-RETURN-CD                        KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFSPRC                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFDTTM                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFSPRC-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFSPRC                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFSPRC-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFDTTM-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFDTTM                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFDTTM-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST.                                            KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK06.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFSPRC.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK07.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFDTTM.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK08.                                               KDS08257

           SELECT JOBSUB    ASSIGN         TO JOBSUB                    KDS08257

           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFAPSB                  KDS08257

       FD JOBSUB.                                                       KDS08257
       01 JOBSUB-REC                     PIC   X(80).                   KDS08257
       FD DATECNTL.                                                     KDS08257
           COPY DTCCNTL.                                                KDS08257
       FD JCSFMAST.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBMAST-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAST==.       KDS08257
       FD JCSFJOBH.                                                     KDS08257
           COPY JCSCJOBH.                                               KDS08257
       FD JCSFDTTM.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBDTTM-REC.                                                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-DTE                    PIC X(08).                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-TME                    PIC X(08).                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-RMD                    PIC X(64).                  KDS08257
      ******************************************************************KDS08257
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                         KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK02.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK00.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK03.                                                   KDS08257
       01 JCBMAS1-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAS1==.       KDS08257
       01 JCBMAS2-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAS2==.       KDS08257
       01 WS-PROC                     PIC  X(08).                       KDS08257
       01 MAX                         PIC  9(03) COMP.                  KDS08257
       01 WS-AP-SYSID                 PIC  X(08).                       KDS08257
       01 PARM-FROM-PGM.                                                KDS08257
        05 PRM-IND                      PIC X(1).                       KDS08257
        05 PRM-SYSID-PGM                PIC X(8).                       KDS08257
        05 PRM-PROC-PGM                 PIC X(8).                       KDS08257
        05 PRM-FROM-PGM                 PIC X(8).                       KDS08257
        05 PRM-RERUN-PGM                PIC 9(2).                       KDS08257
       LINKAGE SECTION.                                                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
         05 PARM-LENGTH          PIC S9(4) COMP.                        KDS08257
         05 PARM-TEXT.                                                  KDS08257
            15 PARM-AP-SYSID     PIC X(08).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-PROC         PIC X(08).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-RC           PIC 9(02).                             KDS08257
            15 PRM-MOD           PIC X(01).                             KDS08257
            15 PRM-SKIP          PIC X(01).                             KDS08257
            15 PRM-FLG           PIC X(01).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-PLUS         PIC X(77).                             KDS08257
       01 FILLER REDEFINES PARM-TO-MAIN.                                KDS08257
            15 PARM-SKIP-K       PIC X(01).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-AP-SYSID-K   PIC X(08).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-PROC-K       PIC X(08).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-PLUS-K       PIC X(91).                             KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBAPNM BEGIN '                                    KDS08257
           PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                      KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                        KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK05.                                               KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = ZERO                                    KDS08257
              IF PARM-SKIP-K = K                                        KDS08257
                 MOVE PARM-PROC-K        TO WS-PROC                     KDS08257
                 MOVE PARM-AP-SYSID-K    TO WS-AP-SYSID                 KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
                 MOVE PARM-PROC          TO WS-PROC                     KDS08257
                 MOVE PARM-AP-SYSID      TO WS-AP-SYSID                 KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              IF WS-PROC = JCSPEND                                      KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'End running sheduler job'  UPON CONSOLE       KDS08257
      *          MOVE WARN               TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM D000-MAIN-PROCESS                                 KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'No job to process'                               KDS08257
              MOVE WARN                  TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY ':: JCSBAPNM  END ::'                                KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D000-MAIN-PROCESS.                                               KDS08257
           PERFORM D001-READ-DATECNTL                                   KDS08257
           MOVE 0             TO WS-I                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM R001-READ-JCSFJOBH                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFJOBH-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-I = WS-I + 1                                   KDS08257
              IF (LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80) >= WS-I             KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBHD-CONTENT         TO WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)        KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM R001-READ-JCSFJOBH                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-I                        TO WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT          KDS08257
           IF WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80        KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'THE JOB HEAD''S NO IS ERROR'                     KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM R002-READ-JCSFMAST                                   KDS08257
           IF JCBMAS1-SUCC-JOB-CNT = ZERO AND                           KDS08257
              JCBMAS1-END-JOB-IND = WS-YES                              KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'No sucessive job to process'                     KDS08257
              MOVE 'JCSPEND'                TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(3:8)      KDS08257
              MOVE 'JCSPEND'                TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(35:8)     KDS08257
              MOVE 'JCSPEND'                TO WS-HEAD-JCL(11)(38:8)    KDS08257
              MOVE SPACE                    TO WS-HEAD-JCL(7)(25:50)    KDS08257
              PERFORM VARYING WS-K FROM 1 BY 1                          KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-K > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80             KDS08257
                  WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-K)               KDS08257
                  DISPLAY 'WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-K)=' WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-K)        KDS08257
                  IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                         KDS08257
                    DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS    KDS08257
                    MOVE ERROR8    TO WS-RETURN-CD                      KDS08257
                    PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                               KDS08257
                 END-IF                                                 KDS08257
              END-PERFORM                                               KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM END-RUN-JCS-JCL                     KDS08257
TSTKDS        DISPLAY 'END TO RUN BATCH'   UPON CONSOLE                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           COMPUTE MAX = JCBMAS1-SUCC-JOB-CNT                           KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
                   UNTIL WS-I > MAX                                     KDS08257
              PERFORM R003-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'CNTX=' JCBMAS1-SUCC-JOB-CNT ':' WS-I             KDS08257
              IF WS-I NOT > JCBMAS1-SUCC-JOB-CNT                        KDS08257
                 MOVE WS-YES                TO WS-CHK-PREV-JOB          KDS08257
                 PERFORM D010-CHECK-SUCCESS-JOB                         KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-I999=' WS-I                                   KDS08257
           END-PERFORM.                                                 KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D001-READ-DATECNTL.                                              KDS08257
           READ DATECNTL                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-DATECNTL-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE DATECNTL ERROR CODE=' WS-DATECNTL-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8                    TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           READ JCSFDTTM                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFDTTM-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFDTTM ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFDTTM-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D010-CHECK-SUCCESS-JOB.                                          KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'Success job=' JCBMAS2-JOB ' WS-PROC=' WS-PROC       KDS08257
TSTKDS*         ' CNT=' JCBMAS2-PREV-JOB-CNT                            KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-J  FROM 1 BY 1                            KDS08257
                   UNTIL WS-J > JCBMAS2-PREV-JOB-CNT                    KDS08257
              IF JCBMAS2-PREV-JOB-STS(WS-J) NOT = S                     KDS08257
                 IF JCBMAS2-PREV-JOB(WS-J) = WS-PROC                    KDS08257
                    MOVE S               TO JCBMAS2-PREV-JOB-STS(WS-J)  KDS08257
                    REWRITE JCBMAST-REC  FROM JCBMAS2-REC               KDS08257
                 ELSE                                                   KDS08257
                    MOVE WS-NO           TO WS-CHK-PREV-JOB             KDS08257
                 END-IF                                                 KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           IF WS-CHK-PREV-JOB = WS-YES AND JCBMAS2-JOB-STATUS = SPACE   KDS08257
              AND JCBMAS2-AUTO-TRIGER = WS-YES AND JCBMAS2-STS = ACT    KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              PERFORM D200-BEGIN-RUN-JOB                                KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       R001-READ-JCSFJOBH.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFJOBH                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFJOBH ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFJOBH-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8                    TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       R002-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PROC              TO JCBMAST-JOB                     KDS08257
           MOVE WS-AP-SYSID          TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID                KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST  INTO JCBMAS1-REC KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY           KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
                      ' KEY IS ' WS-PROC                                KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF (JCBMAS1-JOB-STATUS NOT = SPACE AND                       KDS08257
               JCBMAS1-JOB-STATUS NOT = A     AND                       KDS08257
               JCBMAS1-JOB-STATUS NOT = K)                              KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY JCBMAS1-JOB                                       KDS08257
               ' INVALID JOB STATUS SHOULD BE SPACE OR A OR K='         KDS08257
              JCBMAS1-JOB-STATUS '=' WS-PROC ' SYSID=' JCBMAS1-AP-SYSID KDS08257
              ' EXEC-ST-TIME=' JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-9                   KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'R002 KEY JCBMAST-JOB=' JCBMAST-JOB                  KDS08257
TSTKDS*            ' OUT =' JCBMAS1-JOB                                 KDS08257
           IF PARM-SKIP-K = K                                           KDS08257
              MOVE K                 TO JCBMAS1-JOB-STATUS              KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE S                 TO JCBMAS1-JOB-STATUS              KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE WS-YYYYMMDD          TO JCBMAS1-EXEC-ED-DATE            KDS08257
           MOVE WS-CUR-TIME          TO JCBMAS1-EXEC-ED-TIME            KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-DTE          TO JCBMAS1-EXEC-ST-DATE-9          KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-TME          TO JCBMAS1-EXEC-ST-TIME-9          KDS08257
           REWRITE JCBMAST-REC FROM JCBMAS1-REC                         KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'REWRITE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS    KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8           TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       R003-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS1-SUCC-JOB(WS-I) TO JCBMAST-JOB                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-AP-SYSID            TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID              KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST KEY =' JCBMAST-KEY ':' WS-I      KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST  INTO JCBMAS2-REC KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY           KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
                     ' KEY IS '  JCBMAST-JOB                            KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
      *D100-CHECK-MAST-JOB.                                             KDS08257
      *    COPY JCSCCHCK.                                               KDS08257
      *    EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D200-BEGIN-RUN-JOB.                                              KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'D200-BEGIN-RUN-JOB JCBMAS2-JOB=' JCBMAS2-JOB        KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(3:8)      KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(35:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(11)(38:8)    KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(7)(25:50)    KDS08257
           MOVE '//*'                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(18)          KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(3:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(17:50)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(4)(20:2)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(10)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(17)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-BEGIN             KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-END               KDS08257
           MOVE WS-AP-SYSID                 TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-JOB                 TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
           MOVE OK                          TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-FROM-MODE                TO WS-PRM-MOD               KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAS2-SKIP-IND            TO WS-PRM-SKIP              KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(5)(32:)     KDS08257
           MOVE WARN                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(11)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(19)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(2)(32:)     KDS08257
           IF NOT OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                        KDS08257
              PERFORM A500-OPEN-JOBSUB                                  KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-K FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-K > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80             KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-K)                   KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-K)=' WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-K)            KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE ERROR8    TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-L FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-L > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-FRAME / LENGTH80            KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-L)=' WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-L)          KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-L)                  KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE ERROR8    TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-CLOSE-FILES-JOBSUB                           KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-CLOSE-FILES-JOBSUB.                                         KDS08257
           CLOSE JOBSUB.                                                KDS08257
           SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO   TO TRUE                                 KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    MOVE 13                TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBAPNM END=' WS-RETURN-CD ' B=' WS-RETURN-CD-B    KDS08257
           PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                     KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A500-OPEN-JOBSUB.                                                KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-O-JOBSUB                                    KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
      *                                                                 KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFDTTM                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-DATECNTL                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFJOBH                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-O-JOBSUB                                    KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFJOBH-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFJOBH                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFJOBH-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-DATECNTL-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE DATECNTL                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-DATECNTL-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              CLOSE JOBSUB                                              KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO     TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFDTTM-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFDTTM                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFDTTM-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST.                                            KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK06.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFDTTM.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK08.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-DATECNTL.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK10.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFJOBH.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK11.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-O-JOBSUB.                                               KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK09.                                               KDS08257
      *================================================================*KDS08257

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                                            KDS08257
      *--------------------*                                            KDS08257
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.                                           KDS08257
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.                                            KDS08257
       FILE-CONTROL.                                                    KDS08257
           SELECT JOBSUB    ASSIGN         TO JOBSUB                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JOBSUB-STS.            KDS08257
           SELECT DATECNTL  ASSIGN         TO DATECNTL                  KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-DATECNTL-STS.          KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFAPSB                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFMAST-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBMAST-KEY.              KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFJOBH  ASSIGN         TO JCSFJOBH                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFJOBH-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBHD-SEQ.                KDS08257
       DATA DIVISION.                                                   KDS08257

       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
         05 PARM-LENGTH          PIC S9(4) COMP.                        KDS08257
         05 PARM-TEXT.                                                  KDS08257
            15 PARM-SYSID        PIC X(08).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-ST-TME       PIC X(06).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-ST-TME-9 REDEFINES PARM-ST-TME PIC 9(06).           KDS08257
            15 PARM-RC           PIC 9(02).                             KDS08257
            15 PARM-PLUS         PIC X(90).                             KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBAPSB BEGIN=' PARM-ST-TME                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*       ' PARM-TEXT=' PARM-TEXT(1:PARM-LENGTH) ' :' PARM-LENGTH   KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH <= 14                                         KDS08257
              MOVE ZERO          TO PARM-ST-TME-9                       KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF PARM-ST-TME IS NOT NUMERIC                             KDS08257
                 MOVE 08                        TO WS-RETURN-CD         KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'INVALID START TIME'                           KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'PARM-ST-TME-9=' PARM-ST-TME-9 ' CUR=' WS-CUR-TIME   KDS08257
           IF PARM-ST-TME-9 = ZERO                                      KDS08257
              CONTINUE                                                  KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              PERFORM UNTIL WS-CUR-TIME >= PARM-ST-TME-9                KDS08257
                  MOVE 30            TO DELAY-AMT                       KDS08257
                  CALL ILBOWAT0 USING DELAY-AMT                         KDS08257
                  ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                          KDS08257
              END-PERFORM                                               KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                      KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                        KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK05.                                               KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY     'WS-CUR-TIME=' WS-CUR-TIME                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-CLOSE-FILES-JOBSUB                           KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = ZERO                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM D000-MAIN-PROCESS                                 KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
             MOVE 08                            TO WS-RETURN-CD         KDS08257
             DISPLAY 'INVALID PARM '                                    KDS08257
             PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                      KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D000-MAIN-PROCESS.                                               KDS08257
           PERFORM D001-READ-DATECNTL                                   KDS08257
           MOVE 0             TO WS-I                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM D002-READ-JCSFJOBH                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFJOBH-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-I = WS-I + 1                                   KDS08257
              IF (LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80) >= WS-I             KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBHD-CONTENT         TO WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)        KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM D002-READ-JCSFJOBH                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-I                        TO WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT          KDS08257
           IF WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80        KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'THE JOB HEAD''S NO IS ERROR'                     KDS08257
              MOVE 9                        TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'END READ JOBH'                                      KDS08257
           PERFORM R001-READ-JCSFMAST                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
              MOVE SPACE                    TO WS-RUN                   KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'PARM-SYSID=' PARM-SYSID                          KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'JCSFMSYSID=' JCBMAST-AP-SYSID                    KDS08257
              IF PARM-SYSID = JCBMAST-AP-SYSID                          KDS08257
                 PERFORM D100-CHECK-MAST-JOB                            KDS08257
TSTKDS*           DISPLAY 'WS-RUN=' WS-RUN '>' JCBMAST-JOB ':'          KDS08257
TSTKDS*           JCBMAST-STS ':' JCBMAST-AUTO-TRIGER ':'               KDS08257
TSTKDS*          JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS                                     KDS08257
                 IF JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS = SPACE AND                      KDS08257
                    JCBMAST-STS      = ACT AND                          KDS08257
                    JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-CNT = ZERO AND                     KDS08257
                    ((JCBMAST-AUTO-TRIGER = WS-YES AND                  KDS08257
                     WS-RUN = WS-YES) OR                                KDS08257
                    (JCBMAST-AUTO-TRIGER = WS-NO  AND                   KDS08257
                     WS-RUN2 = WS-YES))                                 KDS08257
                 THEN                                                   KDS08257
TSTKDS*              DISPLAY '<<< RUN....'                              KDS08257
                     PERFORM D200-BEGIN-RUN-JOB                         KDSKDS08
      *              MOVE 03            TO DELAY-AMT                    KDSKDS08
      *              CALL ILBOWAT0 USING DELAY-AMT                      KDSKDS08
                 END-IF                                                 KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM R001-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D001-READ-DATECNTL.                                              KDS08257
           READ DATECNTL                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-DATECNTL-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE DATECNTL ERROR CODE=' WS-DATECNTL-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D002-READ-JCSFJOBH.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFJOBH                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFJOBH ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFJOBH-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       R001-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257

              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8           TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D100-CHECK-MAST-JOB.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCCHCK.                                               KDS08257
       D200-BEGIN-RUN-JOB.                                              KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(3:8)      KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(35:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(11)(38:8)    KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(7)(25:50)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(3:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(17:50)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(4)(20:2)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(10)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(17)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-BEGIN             KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-END               KDS08257
           MOVE PARM-SYSID                  TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
           MOVE OK                          TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-FROM-MODE                TO WS-PRM-MOD               KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-SKIP-IND            TO WS-PRM-SKIP              KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(5)(32:)     KDS08257
           MOVE WARN                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(11)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(19)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(2)(32:)     KDS08257
           MOVE '//*'                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(18)          KDS08257
           IF NOT OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                        KDS08257
              PERFORM A500-OPEN-JOBSUB                                  KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80             KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)                                 KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)                   KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-FRAME / LENGTH80            KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)                                KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)                  KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-CLOSE-FILES-JOBSUB                           KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257

           CLOSE JOBSUB.                                                KDS08257
           SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO   TO TRUE                                 KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257

           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257

           STOP RUN.                                                    KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257

             DISPLAY 'OPEN JOBSUB FILE FAIL=' WS-JOBSUB-STS             KDS08257

             SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO         TO TRUE                         KDS08257

             SET OPEN-JOBSUB-OK         TO TRUE                         KDS08257

           IF OPEN-DATECNTL-OK                                          KDS08257

              SET OPEN-DATECNTL-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              CLOSE JOBSUB                                              KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO     TO TRUE                            KDS08257

           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFAPSB                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFMAST-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBMAST-KEY.              KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFDTTM  ASSIGN         TO JCSFDTTM                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFDTTM-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL.               KDS08257
       DATA DIVISION.                                                   KDS08257
       FILE SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
       FD JCSFMAST.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBMAST-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAST==.       KDS08257
       FD JCSFDTTM.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBDTTM-REC.                                                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-DTE                    PIC X(08).                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-TME                    PIC X(08).                  KDS08257
          03 JCBDTTM-RMD                    PIC X(64).                  KDS08257
      ******************************************************************KDS08257
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                         KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK02.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK00.                                                   KDS08257
       LINKAGE SECTION.                                                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
          03 PARM-LENGTH                     PIC S9(4) COMP.            KDS08257
          03 PARM-CONTENT.                                              KDS08257
             15 PARM-AP-SYSID                PIC X(08).                 KDS08257
             15 PARM-PROC                    PIC X(08).                 KDS08257
             15 PARM-RC                      PIC 9(02).                 KDS08257
             15 PRM-MOD                      PIC X(01).                 KDS08257
             15 PRM-SKIP                     PIC X(01).                 KDS08257
             15 PRM-FLG                      PIC X(01).                 KDS08257
             15 PARM-PLUS                    PIC X(75).                 KDS08257
      *                                                                 KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                        KDS08257
      *    DISPLAY WS-YYYYMMDD WS-CUR-TIME ':DTETME'                    KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK05.                                               KDS08257
           MOVE PARM-PROC            TO JCBMAST-JOB                     KDS08257
           MOVE PARM-AP-SYSID        TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID                KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST  KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY                            KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
                      ' KEY IS ' PARM-PROC                              KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS NOT = SPACE                            KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY JCBMAST-JOB                                       KDS08257
               ' INVALID JOB STATUS SHOULD BE SPACE ='                  KDS08257
              JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS '=' PARM-PROC ' SYSID=' PARM-AP-SYSID  KDS08257
              ' EXEC-ST-TIME=' JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-9                   KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE WS-YYYYMMDD                  TO JCBDTTM-DTE             KDS08257
           MOVE WS-CUR-TIME                  TO JCBDTTM-TME             KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                        TO JCBDTTM-RMD             KDS08257
           WRITE JCBDTTM-REC                                            KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFDTTM-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'WRITE FILE JCSFDTTM ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFDTTM-STS KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFMAST                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-O-JCSFDTTM                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFDTTM-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFDTTM                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFDTTM-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                     KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD         TO RETURN-CODE                     KDS08257
           STOP RUN.                                                    KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFMAST.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK12.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-O-JCSFDTTM.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK16.                                               KDS08257
