           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFMAST                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFMAST-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBMAST-KEY.              KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFJOBH  ASSIGN         TO JCSFJOBH                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFJOBH-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBHD-SEQ.                KDS08257

       FILE SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
       FD JCSFMAST.                                                     KDS08257

           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAST==.       KDS08257
       FD JCSFJOBH.                                                     KDS08257

      ******************************************************************KDS08257
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                         KDS08257
       01 TEMP                    PIC X(08) VALUE SPACE.                KDS08257
       01 WS-END                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACE.                KDS08257
       01 WS-STOP                 PIC X(01) VALUE SPACE.                KDS08257
       01 WS-CNT1                 PIC 9(04) COMP VALUE 0.               KDS08257
       01 WS-CNT2                 PIC 9(04) COMP VALUE 0.               KDS08257
       01 WS-CNT3                 PIC 9(04) COMP VALUE 0.               KDS08257
       01 WS-CNT4                 PIC 9(04) COMP VALUE 0.               KDS08257
       01 WS-F                    PIC X(64) VALUE SPACE.                KDS08257
       01 WS-P-JOB-TBL REDEFINES WS-F.                                  KDS08257
          05 WS-P-JOB             OCCURS 8 TIMES PIC X(08).             KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK00.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK02.                                                   KDS08257
      *                                                                 KDS08257
       LINKAGE SECTION.                                                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
          03 PARM-LENGTH          PIC S9(4) COMP.                       KDS08257
          03 PARM-SYSID           PIC X(008).                           KDS08257
          03 PARM-CONTENT         PIC X(092).                           KDS08257
      *                                                                 KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBCKAP BEGIN '                                    KDS08257
           PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                      KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                        KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK05.                                               KDS08257
           PERFORM S100-READ-JCSFMAST                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'JCBMAST-JOB=' JCBMAST-JOB                        KDS08257
              IF PARM-SYSID = JCBMAST-AP-SYSID                          KDS08257
                 PERFORM S100-REWRITE-JCSFMAST                          KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM S100-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
      *    IF WS-CNT4 > 0 AND WS-CNT3 = 0                               KDS08257
      *       INITIALIZE JCBMAST-REC                                    KDS08257
      *       MOVE PARM-SYSID             TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID           KDS08257
      *       MOVE JCSPEND                TO JCBMAST-JOB                KDS08257
      *       MOVE ACT                    TO JCBMAST-STS                KDS08257
      *       COMPUTE WS-K = 1                                          KDS08257
      *       PERFORM UNTIL WS-P-JOB(WS-K) = SPACE OR                   KDS08257
      *          WS-K <= LENGTH OF WS-P-JOB-TBL / LENGTH OF WS-P-JOB(1) KDS08257
      *          MOVE WS-P-JOB(WS-K)        TO JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-K)   KDS08257
      *          COMPUTE WS-K = WS-K + 1                                KDS08257
      *       END-PERFORM                                               KDS08257
      *       WRITE JCBMAST-REC                                         KDS08257
      *       IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                           KDS08257
      *          DISPLAY 'WRITE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS   KDS08257
      *          MOVE ERROR8       TO WS-RETURN-CD                      KDS08257
      *          PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
      *       END-IF                                                    KDS08257
      *    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                     KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       S100-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST                                                KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'S100-READ-JCSFMAST=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
      *                                                                 KDS08257
       S100-REWRITE-JCSFMAST.                                           KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'S100-REWRITE-JCSFMAST '                             KDS08257
           COMPUTE WS-CNT4 = WS-CNT4 + 1                                KDS08257
           MOVE 1                           TO WS-I                     KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO WS-J                     KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-END                   KDS08257
           COMPUTE HJK = LENGTH OF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(1) +                KDS08257
                         LENGTH OF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-STS(1)              KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
             UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-GRP / HJK          KDS08257
              IF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-I) NOT = SPACE AND                 KDS08257
                 JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-I) NOT = WS-8-0 AND                KDS08257
                 JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-I) NOT = LOW-VALUE                 KDS08257
              THEN                                                      KDS08257
                 ADD 1                     TO WS-J                      KDS08257
                 MOVE SPACE                TO JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-STS(WS-I)KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              IF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-I) = WS-8-0 OR                     KDS08257
                 JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-I) = LOW-VALUE                     KDS08257
              THEN                                                      KDS08257
                MOVE SPACE                 TO  JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-I)   KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-CNT NOT = WS-J                           KDS08257
              MOVE  4                       TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'INVALID PREVIOUS JOB NO MUST BE ='               KDS08257
               ' JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-CNT=' JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-CNT            KDS08257
               ' REAL PREV JOB NO=' WS-J                                KDS08257
              MOVE WS-J                     TO JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-CNT     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           COMPUTE WS-J = 0                                             KDS08257
           COMPUTE HJK = LENGTH OF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(1)                  KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
             UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-GRP / HJK          KDS08257
              IF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-I) NOT = SPACE AND                 KDS08257
                 JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-I) NOT = ALL ZERO AND              KDS08257
                 JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-I) NOT = LOW-VALUE                 KDS08257
              THEN                                                      KDS08257
                 ADD 1                      TO WS-J                     KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              IF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-I) = WS-8-0 OR                     KDS08257
                 JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-I) = LOW-VALUE                     KDS08257
              THEN                                                      KDS08257
                 MOVE SPACE                 TO JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-I)   KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT NOT = WS-J                           KDS08257
              MOVE  4                       TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'INVALID PREVIOUS JOB NO MUST BE ='               KDS08257
               ' JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT=' JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT            KDS08257
               ' REAL SUCESS JOB NO=' WS-J                              KDS08257
              MOVE WS-J                     TO JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-JOB = JCSPEND                                     KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-CNT3 = 1                                       KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT = 0                                  KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-K = WS-K + 1                                   KDS08257
              IF WS-K <= LENGTH OF WS-P-JOB-TBL / LENGTH OF WS-P-JOB(1) KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBMAST-JOB           TO WS-P-JOB(WS-K)           KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'TOO MANY PREVIOUS JOBS FOR JCSPEND'           KDS08257
                 MOVE WARN                  TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
      *    IF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT = 0 AND JCBMAST-JOB NOT = JCSPEND    KDS08257
      *        MOVE K1                      TO JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-CNT     KDS08257
      *        MOVE JCSPEND                 TO JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(1)      KDS08257
      *    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST     KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9   KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-9   KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE     KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME     KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS       KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP       KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO JCBMAST-ERROR-CODE       KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO JCBMAST-EXEC-MODE        KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-END                   KDS08257
           COMPUTE WS-CNT1 = LENGTH OF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-GRP / HJK       KDS08257
           COMPUTE WS-CNT2 = LENGTH OF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-GRP / HJK       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'WS-CNT1 WS-CNT12=' WS-CNT1 ':' WS-CNT2
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'PREV-JOB-GRP1=' JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-GRP
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
           UNTIL WS-I > WS-CNT1                                         KDS08257
              PERFORM VARYING WS-J FROM 1 BY 1                          KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-J > WS-CNT1 - 1                                  KDS08257
                IF JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-J)                               KDS08257
                   < JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-J + 1)                         KDS08257
                THEN                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*            DISPLAY 'XCHANGE PREV JOB '
                   MOVE JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-J)  TO TEMP                 KDS08257
                   MOVE JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-J + 1)                      KDS08257
                     TO JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-J)                          KDS08257
                   MOVE TEMP                                            KDS08257
                     TO JCBMAST-PREV-JOB(WS-J + 1)                      KDS08257
               END-IF                                                   KDS08257
             END-PERFORM                                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'PREV-JOB-GRP2=' JCBMAST-PREV-JOB-GRP
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'SUCC-JOB-GRP1=' JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB-GRP
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
           UNTIL WS-I > WS-CNT2                                         KDS08257
              PERFORM VARYING WS-J FROM 1 BY 1                          KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-J > WS-CNT2 - 1                                  KDS08257
                IF JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-J)                               KDS08257
                   < JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-J + 1)                         KDS08257
                THEN                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*            DISPLAY 'XCHANGE SUCC JOB '
                   MOVE JCBMAST-SUCC-JOB(WS-J)  TO TEMP                 KDS08257

JCSBCKRC.text:
/**** REXX ***********************************************************/
/* Rexx                                                              */
/* Created   By :Kang Dengsong                                       */
/* Created Date :SEP 13, 2008                                        */
/* REMARK       :Job scheduler system                                */
/* ***************************************************************** */
/*================================================================*  */
/* KKKKKKKKKKKKK   DDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS                           *  */
/* KKKKKKKKKKKKK  DDDDDDDDD   SSSSSSSSS                           *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS                                *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS                                *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDD        SSSS          1111          0000000 *  */
/*      KKKK      DDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS      1111        0000000000*  */
/*      KKKK        DDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS     1111        0000  0000*  */
/*      KKKK           DDDD        SSSS    1111         0000  0000*  */
/*      KKKK           DDDD        SSSS    1111        0000  0000 *  */
/*      KKKK           DDDD        SSSS    1111        0000  0000 *  */
/* KKK  KKKK           DDDD        SSSS   1111   0000  0000  0000 *  */
/* KKKKKKKK      DDDDDDDDDD   SSSSSSSSS   1111  0000  0000000000  *  */
/* KKKKKKKK      DDDDDDDDD    SSSSSSSS    1111 0000    000000000  *  */
/*================================================================*  */
ARG JOBNAME
Address TSO
Numeric digits 64
@tcb = Get_dec_addr(540)
@jscb = Get_dec_addr(@tcb+180)
step# = Get_stor_contents(@jscb+X2d(E4) 1)
step# = X2d(C2x(step#))
@jct = Get_dec_addr(@jscb+260)
@sct = Get_dec_addr(@jct+48 3)

last_step = 'NO'
j = 1
If step# = 1 Then
  Do
    Say 'this is the first step; no rc so far --- '
    Exit
  End
Else
  Do While last_step = 'NO'
    sct_abnd = Get_Stor_Contents(@sct+176 1)
    sct_cond = Get_Stor_Contents(@sct+188 1)
    sct_rc = Get_Stor_Contents(@sct+24 2)
    If j < step# Then
      Do
        dec_Rc = Right(X2d(C2x(sct_rc)),4,'0')
        hex_Rc = C2x(sct_rc)
        prf = '8'
        ltrl = ' Rc(hex):    'hex_Rc ' Rc(dec): 'dec_Rc
      End
    Else If j = step# Then
      Do
        dec_Rc = '***'
        hex_Rc = '***'
        prf = '>'
        ltrl = ' *currently executing step* 0000'
      End
    Else
      Do
        dec_Rc = 'n/a'
        hex_Rc = 'n/a'
        prf = '1'
        ltrl = ' ***waiting for execution** WAIT'
      End
    stpnam = Get_stor_contents(@sct+68 8)
    pgmnam = Get_stor_contents(@sct+124 8)
    stpnum = Right(j,3,'0')
    lprf = prf'Schtepp 'stpnum' Stepname: 'stpnam ' Pgmname: 'pgmnam
    If Bitand(sct_cond,'10'X) = '10'X Then     /* COND-Bypass */
      ltrl = ' ***bypassed due to cond*** NOTR'
    If Bitand(sct_abnd,'04'X) = '04'X Then     /* Step Abended */
      ltrl = ' **** Jobstep abended ***** 9999'
    line = lprf''ltrl
    Say line
    @sct = Get_dec_addr(@sct+36 3)        /* sct next step */
    If @sct = 0 Then
      last_step = 'YES'
    j = j + 1
  End
RETURN
Exit
Get_dec_addr:
Parse arg value len
If len = '' Then
  len = 4
hex_value = D2x(value)
stor = Storage(hex_value,len)
hex_stor = C2x(stor)
value = X2d(hex_stor)
Return value
/* */
Get_stor_contents:
arg value length
hex_value = D2x(value)
value = Storage(hex_value,length)
Return value

                 MOVE 9                     TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
                 PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                               KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE 1                       TO WS-I                         KDS08257
           PERFORM D004-READ-JCSFMAST                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'JCBMAST-JOB=' JCBMAST-JOB                        KDSKDS08
              IF PARM-SYSID = JCBMAST-AP-SYSID                          KDSKDS08
                 PERFORM D100-CHECK-MAST-JOB                            KDSKDS08
TSTKDS           DISPLAY JCBMAST-JOB 'WS-RUN=' WS-RUN                   KDSKDS08
TSTKDS             ' JOB ST=' JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS ' WS-RUN2=' WS-RUN2    KDSKDS08
TSTKDS          ' FREQ=' JCBMAST-EXEC-FREQ1 ' ST='                      KDSKDS08
TSTKDS           JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE                                   KDSKDS08
                 IF JCBMAST-STS = ACT AND                               KDSKDS08
                   ((JCBMAST-AUTO-TRIGER = WS-YES AND                   KDSKDS08
                      WS-RUN = WS-YES) OR                               KDS08257
                   (JCBMAST-AUTO-TRIGER = WS-NO AND WS-RUN2 = WS-YES))  KDS08257
                 THEN                                                   KDS08257
                    PERFORM D200-PREPARE-RUN-JOB                        KDSKDS08
TSTKDS              DISPLAY JCBMAST-JOB ' SUBMIT!'                      KDSKDS08
                 END-IF                                                 KDSKDS08
              END-IF                                                    KDSKDS08
              PERFORM D004-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'D000-MAIN-PROCESS END'                              KDSKDS08
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D001-READ-DATECNTL.                                              KDS08257
           READ DATECNTL                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-DATECNTL-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE DATECNTL ERROR CODE=' WS-DATECNTL-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           DISPLAY 'DATECNTL-TWD=' DATECNTL-TWD                         KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D002-READ-JCSFJOBH.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFJOBH                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFJOBH ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFJOBH-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*D003-READ-JCSFFRAM.                                              KDS08257
TSTKDS*    READ JCSFFRAM                                                KDS08257
TSTKDS*    IF WS-JCSFFRAM-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
TSTKDS*       WS-JCSFFRAM-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFFRAM ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFFRAM-STS  KDS08257
TSTKDS*       MOVE  ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                   KDS08257
TSTKDS*       PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
TSTKDS*    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D004-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE ERROR8            TO WS-RETURN-CD                    KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D100-CHECK-MAST-JOB.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCCHCK.                                               KDS08257
       D200-PREPARE-RUN-JOB.                                            KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(3:8)      KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(35:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(11)(38:8)    KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(7)(25:50)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(3:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(17:50)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(4)(20:2)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(10)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(17)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE PARM-SYSID                  TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-BEGIN             KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-END               KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
           MOVE OK                          TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-FROM-MODE                TO WS-PRM-MOD               KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-SKIP-IND            TO WS-PRM-SKIP              KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(5)(32:)     KDS08257
           MOVE WARN                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
      *    MOVE WS-CUR-TIME-9               TO WS-PRM-ST-TME            KDS08257
      *    MOVE WS-YYYYMMDD-9               TO WS-PRM-ST-DTE            KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(11)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(19)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(2)(32:)     KDS08257
           IF NOT OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY '2A500-OPEN-JOBSUB'                               KDS08257
              PERFORM A500-OPEN-JOBSUB                                  KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB     ' WS-CUR-TIME                      KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80             KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)=' WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)            KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)                   KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-FRAME / LENGTH80            KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)=' WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)          KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)                  KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-CLOSE-FILES-JOBSUB                           KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
      *    COMPUTE DELAY-AMT = 3                                        KDS08257
      *    CALL ILBOWAT0 USING DELAY-AMT                                KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-CLOSE-FILES-JOBSUB.                                         KDS08257
           CLOSE JOBSUB.                                                KDS08257
           SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO   TO TRUE                                 KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBMAST END  WS-RETURN-CD=' WS-RETURN-CD           KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A500-OPEN-JOBSUB.                                                KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-O-JOBSUB.                                   KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-O-JOBSUB.                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFMAST.                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFJOBH.                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-DATECNTL.                                 KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFJOBH-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFJOBH                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFJOBH-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              CLOSE JOBSUB                                              KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO     TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-O-JOBSUB.                                               KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK09.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFMAST.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK12.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFJOBH.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK11.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-DATECNTL.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK10.                                               KDS08257

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.                                            KDS08257
      *--------------------*                                            KDS08257
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.                                           KDS08257
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.                                            KDS08257
       FILE-CONTROL.                                                    KDS08257
           SELECT JOBSUB    ASSIGN         TO JOBSUB                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JOBSUB-STS.            KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFAPSB                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFMAST-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBMAST-KEY.              KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFSTEP  ASSIGN         TO JCSFSTEP                  KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBST-KEY                 KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFSTEP-STS.          KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFJOBH  ASSIGN         TO JCSFJOBH                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFJOBH-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBHD-SEQ.                KDS08257
       DATA DIVISION.                                                   KDS08257
       FILE SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
       FD JOBSUB.                                                       KDS08257
       01 JOBSUB-REC                     PIC   X(80).                   KDS08257
       FD JCSFMAST.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBMAST-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAST==.       KDS08257
       FD JCSFSTEP.                                                     KDS08257
           COPY JCSCJBST.                                               KDS08257
       FD JCSFJOBH.                                                     KDS08257
           COPY JCSCJOBH.                                               KDS08257
      ******************************************************************KDS08257
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                         KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK00.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK02.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK03.                                                   KDS08257
       01 WS-PROCSTEP                        PIC X(08) VALUE SPACE.     KDS08257
       LINKAGE SECTION.                                                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
          03 PARM-FROM-JCL.                                             KDS08257
             04 PARM-LENGTH                  PIC S9(4) COMP.            KDS08257
             04 PARM-CONTENT.                                           KDS08257
                05 PRM-SYSID                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
                05 PRM-PROC                  PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
                05 FILLER                    PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
          03 PARM-FROM-PGM REDEFINES PARM-FROM-JCL.                     KDS08257
             05 PRM-IND                      PIC X(1).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-SYSID-PGM                PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-PROC-PGM                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-FROM-PGM                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBRERA BEGIN PARM-TO-MAIN=' PARM-FROM-PGM         KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = 0                                       KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                              KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                     KDS08257
              COPY JCSCWK05.                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                   KDS08257
              PERFORM D001-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
              PERFORM D002-PROCESS-JCSFJOBH                             KDS08257
              PERFORM D005-PREPARE-SUBJCL                               KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO JOB TO PROCESS OR PARM IS INVALID'            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                     KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D001-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           IF PRM-IND = WS-YES
              MOVE PRM-PROC-PGM          TO JCBMAST-JOB                 KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID-PGM         TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID            KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-PROC              TO JCBMAST-JOB                 KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID             TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY                             KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE2 AND                       KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = LENGTHERR                           KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE OR END-FILE2                KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'READ FILE NOT FOUND KEY IS= ' JCBMAST-JOB     KDS08257
                 MOVE  10               TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS NOT = A AND PRM-IND NOT = WS-YES       KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO NEED TO RERUN'                                KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8               TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB             TO JCBST-PROC                   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP      TO JCBST-STEPNAME               KDS08257
           READ JCSFSTEP KEY IS JCBST-KEY                               KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = END-FILE2 AND                       KDS08257
              WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = LENGTHERR                           KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFSTEP ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFSTEP-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8               TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFSTEP-STS = END-FILE OR                          KDS08257
                 WS-JCSFSTEP-STS = END-FILE2                            KDS08257
              THEN                                                      KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'NOT FOUND ERROR ST STEP'                      KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP TO WS-RERUN-STEP               KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'FOUND ERROR ST STEP=' JCBST-ERR-ST-STEP       KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBST-ERR-ST-STEP  TO WS-RERUN-STEP               KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D002-PROCESS-JCSFJOBH.                                           KDS08257
           PERFORM D003-READ-JCSFJOBH                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFJOBH-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-I = WS-I + 1                                   KDS08257
              IF (LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80) >= WS-I             KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBHD-CONTENT      TO WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)           KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM D003-READ-JCSFJOBH                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-I                     TO WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT             KDS08257
           IF WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80        KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'THE JOB HEAD''S NO IS ERROR'                     KDS08257
              MOVE 9                     TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D003-READ-JCSFJOBH.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFJOBH                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFJOBH ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFJOBH-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D005-PREPARE-SUBJCL.                                             KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(3:8)      KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(35:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(11)(38:8)    KDS08257
           IF PRM-FROM-PGM NOT = SPACE AND WS-RERUN-STEP = SPACE        KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-FROM-PGM             TO WS-RERUN-STEP            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF WS-RERUN-STEP = JCSPBGAP OR JCSPWARA OR JCSPWELA          KDS08257
                              OR JCSPABDA                               KDS08257
              IF WS-RERUN-STEP = JCSPBGAP                               KDS08257
                 MOVE SPACE             TO WS-STRING                    KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
                 MOVE WS-RERUN-STEP     TO WS-PROCSTEP                  KDS08257
                 STRING ',RESTART=' WS-PROCSTEP '.'                     KDS08257
                     WS-RERUN-STEP DELIMITED BY SPACE                   KDS08257
                                        INTO WS-STRING                  KDS08257
                 END-STRING                                             KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE JCBMAST-JOB          TO WS-PROCSTEP                  KDS08257
              STRING ',RESTART=' WS-PROCSTEP '.'                        KDS08257
                  WS-RERUN-STEP  DELIMITED BY SPACE                     KDS08257
                                     INTO WS-STRING                     KDS08257
              END-STRING                                                KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE WS-STRING                   TO WS-HEAD-JCL(7)(25:50)    KDS08257
           MOVE '//*'                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(18)          KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(3:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(18:50)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(4)(20:2)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(10)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(17)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-BEGIN             KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-END               KDS08257
           IF PRM-IND = WS-YES
              MOVE PRM-PROC-PGM             TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID-PGM            TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-PROC                 TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID                TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE OK                          TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-PRM-MOD               KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-SKIP-IND            TO WS-PRM-SKIP              KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(5)(32:)     KDS08257
           MOVE WARN                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(11)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(19)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(2)(32:)     KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB     ' WS-CUR-TIME                      KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80             KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)=' WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)            KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)                   KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-FRAME / LENGTH80            KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)=' WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)          KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)                  KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBRERA END WS-RETURN-CD=' WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257

           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFJOBH-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFJOBH                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFJOBH-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFSTEP-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFSTEP                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFSTEP-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              CLOSE JOBSUB                                              KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO     TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257

       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.                                     KDS08257
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.                                            KDS08257
       FILE-CONTROL.                                                    KDS08257
           SELECT JOBSUB    ASSIGN         TO JOBSUB                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JOBSUB-STS.            KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFMAST  ASSIGN         TO JCSFMAST                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFMAST-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBMAST-KEY.              KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFSTEP  ASSIGN         TO JCSFSTEP                  KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS RANDOM                    KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBST-KEY                 KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFSTEP-STS.          KDS08257
           SELECT JCSFJOBH  ASSIGN         TO JCSFJOBH                  KDS08257
                            FILE STATUS    IS WS-JCSFJOBH-STS           KDS08257
                            ACCESS MODE    IS SEQUENTIAL                KDS08257
                            ORGANIZATION   IS INDEXED                   KDS08257
                            RECORD KEY     IS JCBHD-SEQ.                KDS08257
       DATA DIVISION.                                                   KDS08257
       FILE SECTION.                                                    KDS08257

       01 JOBSUB-REC                     PIC   X(80).                   KDS08257
       FD JCSFMAST.                                                     KDS08257
       01 JCBMAST-REC.                                                  KDS08257
           COPY JCSCMAST  REPLACING ==:JCBMAST:== BY ==JCBMAST==.       KDS08257
       FD JCSFSTEP.                                                     KDS08257
           COPY JCSCJBST.                                               KDS08257
       FD JCSFJOBH.                                                     KDS08257
           COPY JCSCJOBH.                                               KDS08257

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.                                         KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK00.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK02.                                                   KDS08257
       COPY JCSCWK01.                                                   KDS08257
       01 WS-PROCSTEP                        PIC X(08) VALUE SPACE.     KDS08257
       LINKAGE SECTION.                                                 KDS08257
       01 PARM-TO-MAIN.                                                 KDS08257
          03 PARM-FROM-JCL.                                             KDS08257
             04 PARM-LENGTH                  PIC S9(4) COMP.            KDS08257
             04 PARM-CONTENT.                                           KDS08257
                05 PRM-SYSID                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
                05 PRM-PROC                  PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
                05 FILLER                    PIC X(08).                 KDS08257
          03 PARM-FROM-PGM REDEFINES PARM-FROM-JCL.                     KDS08257
             05 PRM-IND                      PIC X(1).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-SYSID-PGM                PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-PROC-PGM                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
             05 PRM-FROM-PGM                 PIC X(8).                  KDS08257
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBRERM BEGIN PARM-TO-MAIN=' PARM-FROM-PGM         KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = 0                                       KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                              KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                     KDS08257
              COPY JCSCWK05.                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                   KDS08257
              PERFORM D001-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
              PERFORM D002-PROCESS-JCSFJOBH                             KDS08257
              PERFORM D005-PREPARE-SUBJCL                               KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO JOB TO PROCESS OR PARM IS INVALID'            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                     KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBRERM END'                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
      *    IF PRM-RERUN-PGM-X IS NOT NUMERIC                            KDS08257
      *       MOVE 8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                       KDS08257
      *       DISPLAY 'Invalid parm rerun cnt should be numeric'        KDS08257
      *       PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
      *    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D001-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           IF PRM-IND = WS-YES
              MOVE PRM-PROC-PGM          TO JCBMAST-JOB                 KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID-PGM         TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID            KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-PROC              TO JCBMAST-JOB                 KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID             TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY                             KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE2 AND                       KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = LENGTHERR                           KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE OR END-FILE2                KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'READ FILE NOT FOUND KEY IS= ' JCBMAST-JOB     KDS08257
                 MOVE  10               TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS NOT = A AND PRM-IND NOT = WS-YES       KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO NEED TO RERUN'                                KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8               TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB             TO JCBST-PROC                   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP      TO JCBST-STEPNAME               KDS08257
           READ JCSFSTEP KEY IS JCBST-KEY                               KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = END-FILE2 AND                       KDS08257
              WS-JCSFSTEP-STS NOT = LENGTHERR                           KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFSTEP ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFSTEP-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8               TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFSTEP-STS = END-FILE OR                          KDS08257
                 WS-JCSFSTEP-STS = END-FILE2                            KDS08257
              THEN                                                      KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'NOT FOUND ERROR ST STEP'                      KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP TO WS-RERUN-STEP               KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'FOUND ERROR ST STEP=' JCBST-ERR-ST-STEP       KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBST-ERR-ST-STEP  TO WS-RERUN-STEP               KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D002-PROCESS-JCSFJOBH.                                           KDS08257
           PERFORM D003-READ-JCSFJOBH                                   KDS08257
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-JCSFJOBH-STS = END-FILE                     KDS08257
              COMPUTE WS-I = WS-I + 1                                   KDS08257
              IF (LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80) >= WS-I             KDS08257
                 MOVE JCBHD-CONTENT      TO WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)           KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM D003-READ-JCSFJOBH                                KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           MOVE WS-I                     TO WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT             KDS08257
           IF WS-JOB-HEAD-CNT > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80        KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'THE JOB HEAD''S NO IS ERROR'                     KDS08257
              MOVE 9                     TO WS-RETURN-CD                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D003-READ-JCSFJOBH.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFJOBH                                                KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFJOBH-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFJOBH ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFJOBH-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8                   TO WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D005-PREPARE-SUBJCL.                                             KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(3:8)      KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(1)(35:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-HEAD-JCL(11)(38:8)    KDS08257
           IF PRM-FROM-PGM NOT = SPACE  AND WS-RERUN-STEP = SPACE       KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-FROM-PGM             TO WS-RERUN-STEP            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF WS-RERUN-STEP = JCSPBEGN OR JCSPWARM OR JCSPWELM          KDS08257
                              OR JCSPABDM                               KDS08257
              IF WS-RERUN-STEP = JCSPBEGN                               KDS08257
                 MOVE SPACE             TO WS-STRING                    KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
                 MOVE WS-RERUN-STEP     TO WS-PROCSTEP                  KDS08257
                 STRING ',RESTART=' WS-PROCSTEP '.'                     KDS08257
                     WS-RERUN-STEP DELIMITED BY SPACE                   KDS08257
                                        INTO WS-STRING                  KDS08257
                 END-STRING                                             KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE JCBMAST-JOB          TO WS-PROCSTEP                  KDS08257
              STRING ',RESTART=' WS-PROCSTEP '.'                        KDS08257
                  WS-RERUN-STEP  DELIMITED BY SPACE                     KDS08257
                                     INTO WS-STRING                     KDS08257
                 END-STRING                                             KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE WS-STRING                   TO WS-HEAD-JCL(7)(25:50)    KDS08257
           MOVE '//*'                       TO WS-HEAD-JCL(18)          KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(3:8)     KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-JOB                 TO WS-FRAME-JCL(3)(18:50)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(4)(20:2)    KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(10)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-MAX-ACEPT-RC        TO WS-FRAME-JCL(17)(22:2)   KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-BEGIN             KDS08257
           MOVE ''''                        TO WS-PRM-END               KDS08257
           IF PRM-IND = WS-YES
              MOVE PRM-PROC-PGM             TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID-PGM            TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-PROC                 TO WS-PRM-PROC              KDS08257
              MOVE PRM-SYSID                TO WS-PRM-SYSID             KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE OK                          TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE SPACE                       TO WS-PRM-MOD               KDS08257
           MOVE JCBMAST-SKIP-IND            TO WS-PRM-SKIP              KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(5)(32:)     KDS08257
           MOVE WARN                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(11)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE ZERO                        TO WS-PRM-ACEPT-RC          KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(19)(32:)    KDS08257
           MOVE WS-PARM-TO-PROC             TO WS-FRAME-JCL(2)(32:)     KDS08257
           ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                                 KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB     ' WS-CUR-TIME                      KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-HEAD / LENGTH80             KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)=' WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)            KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-HEAD-JCL(WS-I)                   KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1                             KDS08257
              UNTIL WS-I > LENGTH OF WS-JOB-FRAME / LENGTH80            KDS08257
TSTKDS*       DISPLAY 'WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)=' WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)          KDS08257
              WRITE JOBSUB-REC FROM WS-FRAME-JCL(WS-I)                  KDS08257
              IF WS-JOBSUB-STS NOT = NORMAL                             KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'WRITE JOBSUB ERROR CODE=' WS-JOBSUB-STS       KDS08257
                 MOVE  ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-PERFORM                                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBRERM END WS-RETURN-CD=' WS-RETURN-CD            KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257
      *COPY JCSPWK03.                                                   KDS08257
      *    EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFMAST                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFJOBH                                  KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-0-JOBSUB                                    KDS08257
           PERFORM T00-OPEN-I-JCSFSTEP                                  KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFJOBH-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFJOBH                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFJOBH-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFSTEP-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFSTEP                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFSTEP-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JOBSUB-OK                                            KDS08257
              CLOSE JOBSUB                                              KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JOBSUB-NO     TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-0-JOBSUB.                                               KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK09.                                               KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-I-JCSFMAST.                                             KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK12.                                               KDS08257
