       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBSTSA BEGIN '                                    KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = LENGTH OF PARM-CONTENT                  KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                              KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                     KDS08257
              COPY JCSCWK05.                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                   KDS08257
              IF PRM-PROC NOT = 'ALL'  AND PRM-PROC NOT = SPACE         KDS08257
                 PERFORM D004-READ-JCSFAPSB                             KDS08257
              ELSE                                                      KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              MOVE WARN                 TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO JOB TO PROCESS OR PARM IS INVALID'            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBSTSA END   '                                    KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A000-INITIALIZE.                                                 KDS08257
           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       D004-READ-JCSFAPSB.                                              KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-SYSID               TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID             KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-PROC                TO JCBMAST-JOB                  KDS08257
           READ JCSFAPSB KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY                             KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE2 AND                       KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = INT                                 KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE OR END-FILE2                KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'READ JCSFMAST NOT FOUND KEY IS= ' JCBMAST-KEY KDS08257
                 MOVE  10               TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-STS                    TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS        KDS08257
           REWRITE JCBMAST-REC                                          KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'REWRITE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS    KDS08257
              MOVE     ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBSTSA END  =' WS-RETURN-CD                       KDS08257
           GOBACK.                                                      KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F100-OPEN-FILES.                                                 KDS08257
           IF NOT  OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                     KDS08257
             OPEN I-O JCSFAPSB                                          KDS08257
             IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                        KDS08257
                WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = INT                               KDS08257
                MOVE ERROR8                 TO WS-RETURN-CD             KDS08257
               DISPLAY 'OPEN FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS KDS08257
                SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO TO TRUE                            KDS08257
                PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                   KDS08257
             ELSE                                                       KDS08257
                SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK TO TRUE                            KDS08257
             END-IF                                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       F200-CLOSE-FILES.                                                KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFAPSB                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257

JCSBWAIT.text:
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. JCSBWAIT.
       AUTHOR. KANG DENGSONG
       DATE-WRITTEN.  07/20/2007.
      *--------------------*
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      *--------------------*
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ES9000.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 ILBOWAT0               PIC X(08) VALUE 'ILBOWAT0'.
       01 DELAY-AMT              PIC 9(08) COMP VALUE 0.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 PARAM-TO-MAIN.
         05 PARM-LENGTH          PIC S9(4) COMP.
         05 PARM-TEXT            PIC X(100).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARAM-TO-MAIN.
       MAIN SECTION.
           IF PARM-TEXT(1:PARM-LENGTH) IS NUMERIC
              MOVE PARM-TEXT(1:PARM-LENGTH)
                TO DELAY-AMT
              CALL ILBOWAT0 USING DELAY-AMT
           ELSE
              MOVE 8              TO RETURN-CODE
              DISPLAY 'INVALID PARM '
           END-IF.
           GOBACK.

      *    SELECT JCSFSPRC  ASSIGN         TO JCSFSPRC                  KDS08257

       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING PARM-TO-MAIN.                           KDS08257
       MAIN SECTION.                                                    KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBWELM BEGIN '                                    KDS08257
           IF PARM-LENGTH NOT = 0                                       KDS08257
              PERFORM A000-INITIALIZE                                   KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-CUR-TIME FROM TIME                              KDS08257
              ACCEPT WS-YYYYMMDD FROM DATE YYYYMMDD                     KDS08257
              COPY JCSCWK05.                                            KDS08257
              PERFORM D004-READ-JCSFMAST                                KDS08257
              PERFORM F200-CLOSE-FILES                                  KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'NO JOB TO PROCESS OR PARM IS INVALID'            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                        KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257

           PERFORM F100-OPEN-FILES                                      KDS08257

       D004-READ-JCSFMAST.                                              KDS08257
           READ JCSFDTTM                                                KDS08257

              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFDTTM ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFDTTM-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-PROC                TO JCBMAST-JOB                  KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-SYSID               TO JCBMAST-AP-SYSID             KDS08257
           READ JCSFMAST KEY IS JCBMAST-KEY                             KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE AND                        KDS08257
              WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = END-FILE2                           KDS08257
           THEN                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS  KDS08257
              MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           ELSE                                                         KDS08257
              IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS = END-FILE OR END-FILE2                KDS08257
                 DISPLAY 'READ FILE NOT FOUND KEY IS= ' JCBMAST-JOB     KDS08257
                 MOVE  10               TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
                 PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                  KDS08257
              END-IF                                                    KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
      *    READ JCSFSPRC                                                KDS08257
      *    IF WS-JCSFSPRC-STS NOT = NORMAL AND                          KDS08257
      *       WS-JCSFSPRC-STS NOT = END-FILE                            KDS08257
      *    THEN                                                         KDS08257
      *       DISPLAY 'READ FILE JCSFSPRC ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFSPRC-STS  KDS08257
      *       MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257

      *       MOVE  ERROR8              TO WS-RETURN-CD                 KDS08257
      *       PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
      *    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF PRM-SKIP = WS-YES AND PRM-ACEPT-RC = WARN                 KDS08257
              MOVE WS-YES                  TO WS-RESP                   KDS08257
              PERFORM UNTIL WS-RESP = WS-YES OR WS-NO                   KDS08257
                 DISPLAY JCBMAST-JOB                                    KDS08257
                        ' HAS WARNING MESSAGE, CONTINUE?(Y/N)'          KDS08257
                       UPON CONSOLE                                     KDS08257
                 ACCEPT WS-RESP FROM CONSOLE                            KDS08257
              END-PERFORM                                               KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-DTE                 TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9   KDS08257
           MOVE JCBDTTM-TME                 TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-9   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-YYYYMMDD                 TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE     KDS08257
           MOVE WS-CUR-TIME                 TO JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME     KDS08257
           IF WS-RESP = WS-YES                                          KDS08257
              MOVE WARN                     TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST     KDS08257
              MOVE S                        TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS       KDS08257
              MOVE SPACE                    TO JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP       KDS08257
              MOVE ZERO                     TO JCBMAST-ERROR-CODE-9     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
      *    IF WS-RESP = WS-NO                                           KDS08257
      *       MOVE ABEND                    TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST-C   KDS08257
      *       MOVE A                        TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS       KDS08257
      *       MOVE JCSFSPRC-STEP            TO JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP       KDS08257
      *       MOVE JCSFSPRC-RC              TO JCBMAST-ERROR-CODE       KDS08257
      *    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF PRM-ACEPT-RC = OK                                         KDS08257
              MOVE OK                       TO JCBMAST-EXEC-RC-LAST     KDS08257
              MOVE S                        TO JCBMAST-JOB-STATUS       KDS08257
              MOVE SPACE                    TO JCBMAST-ERROR-STEP       KDS08257
              MOVE ZERO                     TO JCBMAST-ERROR-CODE-9     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           MOVE PRM-MOD                     TO JCBMAST-EXEC-MODE        KDS08257
           MOVE WS-NO                       TO JCBMAST-RECOVER-STS      KDS08257
           COMPUTE WS-DAYS     =                                        KDS08257
             FUNCTION INTEGER-OF-DATE(JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-DATE-9) -         KDS08257
             FUNCTION INTEGER-OF-DATE(JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-DATE-9)           KDS08257
           COMPUTE JCBMAST-COST-TIME = WS-DAYS * 3600 * 24 +            KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-HH - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-HH)     KDS08257
                + 60 *                                                  KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-MM - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-MM)     KDS08257
                +                                                       KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-SS - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-SS)     KDS08257
                +                                                       KDS08257
                (JCBMAST-EXEC-ED-TIME-MS - JCBMAST-EXEC-ST-TIME-MS)     KDS08257
                / 100                                                   KDS08257
           REWRITE JCBMAST-REC                                          KDS08257
           IF WS-JCSFMAST-STS NOT = NORMAL                              KDS08257
           then                                                         KDS08257
              DISPLAY 'REWRITE JCSFMAST ERROR CODE=' WS-JCSFMAST-STS    KDS08257
              MOVE     ERROR8   TO WS-RETURN-CD                         KDS08257
              PERFORM A300-STOP-RUN                                     KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       A300-STOP-RUN.                                                   KDS08257
           MOVE WS-RETURN-CD      TO RETURN-CODE                        KDS08257
TSTKDS*    DISPLAY 'JCSBWELM END  =' WS-RETURN-CD                       KDS08257
           STOP RUN.                                                    KDS08257
      *    EXIT.                                                        KDS08257

           IF OPEN-JCSFMAST-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFMAST                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFMAST-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
      *    IF OPEN-JCSFSPRC-OK                                          KDS08257
      *       CLOSE JCSFSPRC                                            KDS08257
      *       SET OPEN-JCSFSPRC-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
      *    END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           IF OPEN-JCSFDTTM-OK                                          KDS08257
              CLOSE JCSFDTTM                                            KDS08257
              SET OPEN-JCSFDTTM-NO   TO TRUE                            KDS08257
           END-IF                                                       KDS08257
           EXIT.                                                        KDS08257
       T00-OPEN-IO-JCSFMAST.                                            KDS08257
           COPY JCSCWK06.                                               KDS08257
